# Sample "knows" DSL file — demonstrates foaf:Person coloring, radii, and hull
#
# Load this file via the "Load Title File" button after loading knows-parser.js
# as a custom loader.  All nodes will appear in blue (#4f9cf9) with radius 10
# and a light-blue convex hull around the whole group.

Alice knows Bob.
Alice knows Carol.
Bob knows Dave.
Bob knows Eve.
Carol knows Eve.
Carol knows Frank.
Dave knows Grace.
Eve knows Grace.
Frank knows Henry.
Grace knows Henry.
Henry knows Alice.
